<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">د ح ض:</span> <span class="c2">(دَحَضَتْ)</span> حُجَّتُهُ بَطَلَتْ وَبَابُهُ خَضَعَ وَ <span class="c2">(أَدْحَضَهَا)</span> اللَّهُ. وَ <span class="c2">(دَحَضَتْ)</span> رِجْلُهُ زَلِقَتْ وَبَابُهُ قَطَعَ. وَ <span class="c2">(الْإِدْحَاضُ)</span> الْإِزْلَاقُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>